desc: Storehouse on Market offers a nice selection of rugs, lamps, accent furniture, home goods such as bedding and towels, home decor, greenery and SO MUCH MORE. Located just off the #smalltowntaylorville historic downtown square. Regular business hours are Monday - Saturday 9am - 6pm.

layout.text: Furniture. Rugs. Poufs. Decor. Home Goods. Greenery. So Much More.
